<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 12:22:41 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>印度必须批准 GIFT City 与邻国投资者的上市</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-must-approve-gift-city-listings-with-investors-bordering-nations-2024-01-24/</link><description>根据周三发布的规定，如果一家拥有中国等邻国股东的当地公司想要在新金融中心注册的交易所上市，则需要获得印度政府的批准。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 12:09:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-must-approve-gift-city-listings-with-investors-bordering-nations-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：提振对脆弱中国的信心</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-graphics-2024-01-24/</link><description>达拉·拉纳辛格 (Dhara Ranasinghe) 展望美国和全球市场未来一天</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 11:03:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-graphics-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>郑爽击败卡林斯卡娅晋级澳网半决赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/zheng-finds-groove-down-kalinskaya-reach-australian-open-semis-2024-01-24/</link><description>周三，郑钦文一改开局不利的局面，以6-7(4) 6-3 6-1击败俄罗斯选手安娜·卡林斯卡娅，首次进入澳网半决赛，中国12号种子将迎战乌克兰预选赛选手达亚娜·亚斯特雷姆斯卡。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 10:58:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/zheng-finds-groove-down-kalinskaya-reach-australian-open-semis-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>梅德韦杰夫奋战澳网半决赛，亚斯特雷姆斯卡巡演</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/medvedev-battles-reach-australian-open-semis-yastremska-cruises-2024-01-24/</link><description>丹尼尔·梅德韦杰夫抓住了休伯特·胡尔卡奇提供的为数不多的机会，在周三的澳大利亚网球公开赛上锁定了半决赛席位，而达亚娜·亚斯特雷姆斯卡则首次进入大满贯四强，让新一代人感到自豪。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 10:13:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/medvedev-battles-reach-australian-open-semis-yastremska-cruises-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>调查显示更多德国企业离开中国或考虑退出</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/more-german-firms-leave-china-or-consider-exit-survey-2024-01-24/</link><description>中国德国商会的一项调查显示，过去四年，德国企业退出或考虑退出中国市场的比例增加了一倍多，达到9%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 10:05:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/more-german-firms-leave-china-or-consider-exit-survey-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国反驳越南对南海争议岛屿的主张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-rebuts-vietnams-claims-disputed-south-china-sea-islands-2024-01-24/</link><description>中国外交部周三表示，中国对南海西沙群岛和南沙群岛的主权主张有“历史”支持，此前越南周末重申有足够证据证明对这些岛屿拥有主权。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 10:00:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-rebuts-vietnams-claims-disputed-south-china-sea-islands-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国火箭初创公司东方航天融资近8400万美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/china-rocket-startup-orienspace-raises-nearly-84-mln-2024-01-24/</link><description>中国私营火箭开发商东方航天周三表示，由于中国对卫星商业发射的需求预计将增加，该公司已筹集近 6 亿元人民币（合 8367 万美元）用于火箭开发。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 09:47:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/china-rocket-startup-orienspace-raises-nearly-84-mln-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国恒大海外债券持有人集团将加入清算申请--消息人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-evergrande-offshore-bondholder-group-join-liquidation-petition-sources-2024-01-24/</link><description>两位直接知情人士称，中国恒大的一个主要离岸债券持有人集团计划在周一香港法院的听证会上加入清算该开发商的请愿书。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 09:45:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/china-evergrande-offshore-bondholder-group-join-liquidation-petition-sources-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国提振经济信心的努力失败</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-attempts-lift-confidence-economy-fall-flat-2024-01-24/</link><description>中国总理李强上周出席达沃斯世界经济论坛，其使命是展示中国经济的正面形象并与金融精英进行交流：“投资中国市场不是风险，而是机遇。”</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 09:16:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-attempts-lift-confidence-economy-fall-flat-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>ASML预计美国、荷兰出口规则将使中国销售额下降10-15%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-expects-us-dutch-export-rules-hit-china-sales-by-10-15-2024-01-24/</link><description>荷兰计算机芯片设备制造商ASML周三表示，预计美国和荷兰新的出口限制措施将使其“DUV”产品线今年对中国的销量减少约10%至15%，此前这些产品在2023年创下历史新高。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 08:46:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-expects-us-dutch-export-rules-hit-china-sales-by-10-15-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>即时观点：中国央行采取行动支持市场和经济</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/view-china-central-bank-acts-support-markets-economy-2024-01-24/</link><description>周三，中国央行行长潘功胜表示，中国央行将从 2 月 5 日起削减银行必须持有的现金准备金数额，这是政策制定者加大力度支撑脆弱的经济复苏之际今年的首次削减。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 08:45:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/view-china-central-bank-acts-support-markets-economy-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国承诺提振市场情绪，富时 100 指数上涨，易捷航空攀升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/ftse-100-gains-china-pledges-aid-sentiment-easyjet-climbs-2024-01-24/</link><description>英国蓝筹股指数周三上涨，受到央行采取措施支持经济后中国股市的提振，而易捷航空 (Easyjet) 预计亏损较小，股价飙升。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 08:42:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/ftse-100-gains-china-pledges-aid-sentiment-easyjet-climbs-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲股市因乐观的科技盈利和中国银行援助而上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-shares-open-higher-upbeat-tech-earnings-2024-01-24/</link><description>软件公司 SAP 和芯片制造设备制造商 ASML Holding 公布强劲盈利后，欧洲股市周三走高，受到科技股的提振，而中国央行的新刺激措施进一步提振了市场情绪。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 08:33:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-shares-open-higher-upbeat-tech-earnings-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国削减银行准备金以捍卫市场、刺激增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-will-cut-banks-reserve-ratio-next-month-bolster-economic-recovery-2024-01-24/</link><description>中国央行周三宣布大幅削减银行准备金，此举将向银行体系注入约1400亿美元现金，并发出支持脆弱经济和暴跌股市的强烈信号。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 08:11:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-will-cut-banks-reserve-ratio-next-month-bolster-economic-recovery-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>诺基亚与中国 Oppo 通过交叉许可协议解决纠纷</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/nokia-chinas-oppo-resolve-disputes-through-cross-license-deal-2024-01-24/</link><description>芬兰电信设备制造商诺基亚周三表示，已与中国设备制造商 Oppo 签署了 5G 专利交叉许可协议，解决了两家公司之间的专利诉讼。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 07:23:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/nokia-chinas-oppo-resolve-disputes-through-cross-license-deal-2024-01-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>